!! Percentage-Based Vertical Resizer

<div style="height: 300px; border: 1px solid #ddd; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
<div style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 0.5em; overflow: auto;" style.height={{{ [{$:/state/vertical-percent/height}!is[blank]else[30%]] }}}>
Panel height: {{$:/state/vertical-percent/height}}
</div>
<$resizer
	class="vertical-resizer-handle-2"
	direction="vertical"
	tiddler="$:/state/vertical-percent/height"
	min="10%"
	max="70%"
	default="30%"
	unit="%"
/>
<div style="background: #ddd; padding: 0.5em; flex: 1; overflow: auto;">
Remaining space
</div>
</div>

!! Features

* ''Direction'': Set to "vertical" for up/down resizing
* ''Min/Max'': Constraints work with pixels or percentages
* ''Cursor'': Automatically shows `ns-resize` cursor
* ''Flexible Layouts'': Works with flexbox, grid, or absolute positioning